OL,3,CEngland's local elections will have a
OL,4,Cbig national impact
OL,6,FAhead of next week's local elections
OL,7,Fin England, ITV News Political
OL,8,FCorrespondent Harry Horton has been
OL,9,Fhearing about the challenges facing
OL,10,Fthe leading parties as millions
OL,11,Fprepare to go to the polls
OL,13,FThese elections might be local - but
OL,14,Fthe results will have a national
OL,15,Fimpact.JLabour is defending around
OL,16,Fhalf of the five thousand council
OL,17,Fseats up for election in England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
