OL,3,CEngland's local elections will have a
OL,4,Cbig national impact
OL,6,FHow many seats Labour lose - and
OL,7,Fpollsters say it could more than one
OL,8,Fthousand - will determine Keir
OL,9,FStarmer's immediate political future.
OL,11,FLabour's vote is being split two ways
OL,12,F- on the right to Reform UK and on the
OL,13,Fleft to the Green Party.
OL,15,FNigel Farage is hoping his party will
OL,16,Fbe the big winner in these local
OL,17,Felections.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
