OL,3,CEngland's local elections will have a
OL,4,Cbig national impact
OL,6,FIn Sunderland - where the council has
OL,7,Fbeen run by Labour since its creation
OL,8,Fmore than half a century ago - Reform
OL,9,FUK is hoping to take control.
OL,11,FOutside a Reform UK election rally in
OL,12,Fthe city, one supporter told me:
OL,13,F"we've always voted either Labour or
OL,14,FConservative, but the country's now
OL,15,Fbroken and they've absolutely
OL,16,Fdestroyed everything... the North
OL,17,FEast's always forgotten."
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
