OL,3,CEngland's local elections will have a
OL,4,Cbig national impact
OL,6,FThe Green Party launched its local
OL,7,Felection campaign in another Labour
OL,8,Fheartland - this time in Lewisham,
OL,9,FSouth London. Zack Polanski, the
OL,10,FGreen's new leader, has taken on a
OL,11,Fpopulist approach which has seen the
OL,12,Fparty appeal to younger, more affluent
OL,13,Fvoters in urban areas.
OL,15,FLondon councils like Lambeth, Lewisham
OL,16,Fand Hackney have all been safe Labour
OL,17,Fterritory for decades - but are now
OL,18,Fhigh on the Green's target list.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
