CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777539988
OL,3,CEngland's local elections will have a
OL,4,Cbig national impact
OL,6,FOn East London's Broadway Market -
OL,7,Fhome of artisan bakeries and expensive
OL,8,Fcoffee shops - one first time Green
OL,9,Fvoter told me: "I think Labour's
OL,10,Frhetoric against migrants is really
OL,11,Fhostile and horrible. I was always
OL,12,FLabour, Labour, Labour, but I can no
OL,13,Flonger support them."
OL,15,FNot everyone is convinced, though. One
OL,16,Fman told me he thought Zack Polanski
OL,17,Fwas "a bit naive... It feels like it's
OL,18,Fanother version of what Jeremy Corbyn
OL,19,Fwas suggesting at one level."
OL,26,@qD@POUuD@UO]yD@EOU{D@]O]
