OL,3,CEngland's local elections will have a
OL,4,Cbig national impact
OL,6,FIn Brixton, South London, we joined
OL,7,FLabour's Deputy Leader, Lucy Powell,
OL,8,Fas she campaigned with local members.
OL,9,FWhat does it say about this election
OL,10,Fthat Labour is having to focus its
OL,11,Fcampaigning on once-safe London seats?
OL,13,F"I don't think there's such a thing
OL,14,Fanymore," Ms Powell told me. "Look,
OL,15,Fwe're in midterm of the Labour
OL,16,Fgovernment. It's always going to be
OL,17,Fthe most difficult point to really
OL,18,Fmobilise people and get people out."
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@IO]vD@^OUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
