OL,3,CEngland's local elections will have a
OL,4,Cbig national impact
OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrat and Conservative
OL,7,FParty leaders are also under pressure
OL,8,Fto show they are making progress.
OL,10,FKemi Badenoch's Tory party are still
OL,11,Fpolling behind their final result in
OL,12,Fthe 2024 general election, and are
OL,13,Fbraced for a bad set of results.
OL,15,FAnd some Liberal Democrat MPs feel
OL,16,Ftheir party should be doing more to
OL,17,Ftake advantage of an unpopular Labour
OL,18,Fgovernment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
