OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777539988
OL,3,CEngland's local elections will have a
OL,4,Cbig national impact
OL,6,FThere is another, growing, political
OL,7,Fforce in these elections: independent
OL,8,Fcandidates. Almost four times as many
OL,9,Fare standing this year compared to
OL,10,Fwhen these elections were last held,
OL,11,Faccording to analysis by The Times.
OL,13,FMany - but not all - are standing on a
OL,14,Fpro-Gaza ticket and they could become
OL,15,Fa dominant force on some of England's
OL,16,Fcouncils.
OL,18,FWe have entered a new era of British
OL,19,Fpolitics, according to ITV News
OL,20,Felection analyst Professor Colin
OL,21,FRallings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
