OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777539988
OL,3,CEngland's local elections will have a
OL,4,Cbig national impact
OL,6,F"Not only can multi-party politics
OL,7,Fproduce sometimes rather weird and
OL,8,Falmost random election results, when
OL,9,Fyou add up the outcome at council
OL,10,Flevel you inevitably have a situation
OL,11,Fwhere no one party can run the
OL,12,Fcouncil," he said.
OL,14,F"It makes it hard for the electorate
OL,15,Fto realise quite who has been
OL,16,Fresponsible for delivering the local
OL,17,Fpolicies and then either rewarding
OL,18,Fthem or punishing them at the end of
OL,19,Fthe day."
